comments: Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Harris (ORL) establishes himself in Booker's (PHX) path and marginal contact occurs as they both move toward the basket after the pick.
Carter Jr. (ORL) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) engages and disengages with Carter Jr. (ORL) and marginal contact occurs prior to the pick being set.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Booker's (PHX) path and does not deliver contact.
Okogie (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Carter Jr. (ORL) as the steal occurs.
Carter Jr. (ORL) moves along Okogie's (PHX) path and marginal body contact occurs as he gathers the pass in the lane.
Paul (PHX) and Banchero (ORL) come together off ball and Paul (PHX) deflects the pass attempt before incidental body contact occurs.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Banchero (ORL) is the last person to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds. The possession is correctly given to PHX.
Fultz (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Booker (PHX) prior to incidental arm contact occurring during the drive.

Booker (PHX) slightly extends his arm out and marginal contact occurs to Fultz's (ORL) chin as they pursue the loose ball.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Banchero (ORL) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Booker (PHX) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Booker (PHX) briefly slides his hand down Banchero's (ORL) arm in transition and he is able to move through the marginal contact.
Paul (PHX) briefly places his hand to Banchero's (ORL) side and marginal body contact occurs as he releases his pass attempt.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Harris (ORL) and Paul (PHX) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Suggs (ORL) and Booker (PHX) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Fultz (ORL) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Harris (ORL) commits a take foul on Ross (ORL).
Wainright (PHX) engages and disengages with Carter Jr. (ORL) and marginal contact occurs as they roll to the basket.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Booker's (PHX) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Okogie (PHX) cleanly blocks Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt before incidental arm contact occurs.
Banchero's (ORL) arms come down after the release of his jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Okogie (PHX).
